<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Jemi belok, albumin, mikroelementler we elektrolitler&nbsp;</span></b><span
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>agyr
i&ccedil;ge&ccedil;me we i&ccedil;eg&auml;ni&#328; n&auml;sazlygyna baha bermek
&uuml;&ccedil;in barlan&yacute;ar.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Derejesi&nbsp;<b>disk calprotectin&nbsp;</b>gytakla&yacute;yn
i&ccedil;ege diwary&#328; enflamatuar &uuml;&yacute;tge&#351;meler derejesini
&ccedil;akla&yacute;ar.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Kesgitli &ccedil;i&#351;me bilen &uuml;lser kolitini
tapawutlandyrmak &uuml;&ccedil;in awtoimmun &ccedil;i&#351;mesini&#328;
bellikleri ulanyl&yacute;ar:&nbsp;<b>perinadro antine&yacute;trofil
sitoplazmatiki antikorlary (p-ANCA)&nbsp;</b>we&nbsp;<b>Saccharomyces
serevisiae (ASCA) antikorlary&nbsp;</b>.&nbsp;O&#328;yn ASCA synagy Kesgitli
&ccedil;i&#351;mende has &yacute;ygy du&#351; gel&yacute;&auml;r, p-ANCA bolsa
&uuml;lseratif kolitde has &yacute;ygy du&#351; gel&yacute;&auml;r,
k&auml;mahal Kesgitli &ccedil;i&#351;mende-de bol&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Bular
d&uuml;&#351;n&uuml;ksiz endoskopiki we gistologiki tapyndylara k&ouml;mek edip
biljek k&ouml;mek&ccedil;i synaglar.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Koprogramma&nbsp;</span></b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>, i&yacute;mit
si&#328;diri&#351; mehanizmlerinde n&auml;sazlyklar &yacute;&uuml;ze
&ccedil;ykan halatynda, i&ccedil;eg&auml;ni&#328; diwaryna zeper&nbsp;<b>&yacute;etmegi&#328;&nbsp;</b>alamaty,
i&yacute;mitlenmedik i&yacute;mit komponentleri h&ouml;km&uuml;nde&nbsp;<b>tabakdaky&nbsp;</b>gany
kesgitlem&auml;ge m&uuml;mkin&ccedil;ilik ber&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Endoskopiki synaglar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Kesgitli &ccedil;i&#351;me
kesellerini i&#328; anyk anyklamagy&#328; usullaryna degi&#351;lidir.&nbsp;</span><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Ahyrynda wideo kameraly &yacute;&ouml;rite in&ccedil;e
turbalary&#328; k&ouml;megi bilen amala a&#351;yryl&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Uly
i&ccedil;eg&auml;ni barlamak &uuml;&ccedil;in&nbsp;<b>fibrokolonoskopi&yacute;a&nbsp;</b>,
a&#351;gazan-i&ccedil;ege ulgamyny&#328; &yacute;okarky b&ouml;lekleri
(&ouml;zofagus, a&#351;gazan we on iki&nbsp;<b>barmakly&nbsp;</b>i&ccedil;ege)
-&nbsp;<b>fibrogastroduodenoskopi&yacute;a edil&yacute;&auml;r&nbsp;</b>.&nbsp;Bu
amallary&#328; dowamynda lukman gyjyndyrmany barla&yacute;ar,&nbsp;<b>biopsi&yacute;a
ed&yacute;&auml;r&nbsp;</b>(gistologiki barlag &uuml;&ccedil;in dokumany&#328;
bir b&ouml;legini al&yacute;ar).&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>K&auml;bir hadysalarda
adaty endoskopiki usullara girip bolma&yacute;an in&ccedil;e i&ccedil;egede
patologiki proses &ouml;s&uuml;p biler.&nbsp;So&#328;ra&nbsp;<b>wideo
kapsulasyny &ouml;wrenmek&nbsp;</b>ulanyl&yacute;ar&nbsp;: maglumatlar
hassany&#328; &yacute;uwud&yacute;an wideo kamerasy bilen &yacute;&ouml;rite
kapsuladan iberil&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Adat&ccedil;a
i&ccedil;ege b&ouml;wetlenmesi &yacute;a-da perforasi&yacute;a &yacute;aly
kyn&ccedil;ylyklary anyklamak &uuml;&ccedil;in&nbsp;<b>rentgen
&#351;&ouml;hleleri&nbsp;</b>ulanyl&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Bir bilen&nbsp;<b>irrigoscopy&nbsp;</b>,
baryum s&uuml;lfat (a agymtyl suwuk hamur) we howa i&ccedil;ege i&ccedil;ine
enjekte edilir.&nbsp;Barini&#328; we howany&#328; ikisi hem
i&ccedil;eg&auml;ni&#328; we rektumy&#328; i&ccedil;ki diwaryny&#328;
gurlu&#351;yny g&ouml;rm&auml;ge, &#351;e&yacute;le hem Kesgitli
&ccedil;i&#351;mene mahsus i&ccedil;eg&auml;ni&#328; we t&ouml;weregind&auml;ki
dokumalary&#328; arasyndaky patologiki ge&ccedil;i&#351;leri kesgitlem&auml;ge
m&uuml;mkin&ccedil;ilik ber&yacute;&auml;n rentgen arkaly
g&ouml;r&uuml;n&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Hasaplanan
tomografi&yacute;a&nbsp;</span></b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>we&nbsp;<b>magnit-rezonans
tomografi&yacute;asy&nbsp;</b>, i&ccedil;egede &ccedil;i&#351;me
prosesini&#328; &yacute;a&yacute;ramagyna, garyn bo&#351;lugyny&#328;
be&yacute;leki agzalaryny&#328; &yacute;agda&yacute;yna (bagyr, &ouml;d
&yacute;ollary) baha berm&auml;ge m&uuml;mkin&ccedil;ilik ber&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;</span><span
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Endoskopiki
barlaglary ge&ccedil;irip bilme&yacute;&auml;nler &uuml;&ccedil;in
a&yacute;ratyn m&ouml;h&uuml;mdir.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Bejergi</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Bejergi maksatlary</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Keseli&#328; g&uuml;&yacute;&ccedil;lenmeginden dynmak;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>remissi&yacute;any&#328; m&uuml;mkin bolan i&#328; uzyn hyzmaty;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>kyn&ccedil;ylyklary&#328; &ouml;smegini&#328; &ouml;&#328;&uuml;ni
al&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Durmu&#351; &yacute;oly we
gurallar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>&Ccedil;ilimi
ta&#351;lamak&nbsp;</span></b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>, i&ccedil;eg&auml;ni&#328; &ccedil;i&#351; keselini
gowulandyr&yacute;ar.&nbsp;G&uuml;&yacute;&ccedil;lendirme az
bol&yacute;ar.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Psiho-emosional streslere
g&ouml;zeg&ccedil;ilik etmek&nbsp;</span></b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>hem o&#328;yn t&auml;sir
ed&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Bejergini&#328; ba&#351;langy&ccedil; tapgyrynda
psiholog &yacute;a-da psihoterapewt bilen maslahatla&#351;malar k&ouml;mek edip
biler.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>I&yacute;mitlenmek&nbsp;</span></b><span
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>hem
&ouml;r&auml;n m&ouml;h&uuml;mdir.&nbsp;Agyrla&#351;ma wagtynda berhizd&auml;ki
s&uuml;&yacute;&uuml;mi&#328; mukdaryny azaltmak maslahat
beril&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;S&uuml;&yacute;t &ouml;n&uuml;mleri, alamatlary
erbetle&#351;dirmese, &ccedil;&auml;klendirilme&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Dermanlar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Aminosalisil
tur&#351;usyny&#328; ta&yacute;&yacute;arlyklary&nbsp;</span></b><span
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>,
&ccedil;i&#351;m&auml; gar&#351;y t&auml;sir
ed&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Bulary&#328; ikisi hem agyrla&#351;magy bejermek we
g&uuml;n&auml;sini ge&ccedil;mek &uuml;&ccedil;in
ulanyl&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Olary&#328; bellenmegini&#328; esasy g&ouml;rkezijisi,
&uuml;lseratif kolitdir;&nbsp;t&auml;siri Kesgitli &ccedil;i&#351;me
&uuml;&ccedil;in subut edilmedi.&nbsp;&#350;e&yacute;le-de bolsa,
gl&yacute;ukokortikosteroidlere &ccedil;ydamsyzlyk &yacute;agda&yacute;ynda bu
keselde hem ulanyl&yacute;ar.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Gl&yacute;ukokortikosteroidler&nbsp;</span></b><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>gormonal &ccedil;i&#351;m&auml; gar&#351;y we immunosupressiw
dermanlardyr.&nbsp;Elokan&ccedil; i&ccedil;ege kesellerinde di&#328;e
remissi&yacute;a &uuml;&ccedil;in ulanyl&yacute;ar, ony saklamakdaky
netijeliligi subut edilmedi.&nbsp;Mundan ba&#351;ga-da, kabul edi&#351; fonunda
&ouml;s&yacute;&auml;n zy&yacute;anly t&auml;sirler, bu dermanlar bilen uzak m&ouml;hletli
bejergini&#328; m&uuml;mkin&ccedil;iligini ep-esli
&ccedil;&auml;klendir&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Kortikosteroidler damar we agyz
dozalary g&ouml;rn&uuml;&#351;inde, &#351;e&yacute;le hem rektal
&ccedil;aklamalar we mikroklysterler g&ouml;rn&uuml;&#351;inde
ulanyl&yacute;ar.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Immunosupressiw
dermanlar&nbsp;</span></b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:
"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>immun &ccedil;i&#351;mesini
bas&yacute;ar.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Ti&yacute;opurin toparyny&#328; ta&yacute;&yacute;arlyklary,
&ccedil;i&#351;megi &yacute;ok etmek &uuml;&ccedil;in, &#351;e&yacute;le hem
steroidler bilen bejermekde gazanylan remissi&yacute;any saklamak
&uuml;&ccedil;in &ccedil;i&#351;m&auml; gar&#351;y dermanlar bilen bilelikde
ulanylyp bilner.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Ti&yacute;opurinler i&#351;leme&yacute;&auml;n mahaly metotreksat
ulanyl&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Inflamokan&ccedil;lyga gar&#351;y dermanlar we tiopurinler
netijesiz bolanda kalsinurin ingibitorlary bellenil&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Monoklonal antikorlar
synpyny&#328; dermanlary&nbsp;<b>bilen biologiki bejergi&nbsp;</b>.&nbsp;Immun
&ccedil;i&#351;mesini&#328; &ouml;smegine gatna&#351;&yacute;an esasy belok,
&ccedil;i&#351; nekroz faktoryna gar&#351;y antikorlar
ulanyl&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Bu belogy blokirlemek bilen, dermanlar &ccedil;i&#351;me
prosesini duruzmaga k&ouml;mek ed&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Bu dermanlary
lukmany&#328; g&ouml;zeg&ccedil;iligi astynda bellenilen tertibe
la&yacute;yklykda yzygiderli kabul etmek m&ouml;h&uuml;mdir.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Antibakterial
dermanlar&nbsp;</span></b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:
"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>esasan i&ccedil;ege keselini&#328;
&yacute;okan&ccedil; kyn&ccedil;ylyklaryny bejermek &uuml;&ccedil;in
ulanyl&yacute;ar.&nbsp;</span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Esasy dermanlar metronidazol, siprofloksasin we rifaximin.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Simptomatiki bejergi</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Loperamid&nbsp;</span></b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>agyr i&ccedil;ge&ccedil;me
&uuml;&ccedil;in ulanyl&yacute;ar (lukman bilen maslahatla&#351;mak
zerur);&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>parasetamol&nbsp;</span></b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>agyryny a&yacute;yrmak
&uuml;&ccedil;in ulanylyp bilner;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>&yacute;okumly maddalary&#328; si&#328;dirilmegi &uuml;&ccedil;in
k&ouml;p&nbsp;<b>witaminli toplumlar&nbsp;</b>zerurdyr.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Hirurgiki
amallar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Dermanlar netijesiz bolanda,
keseli&#328; agyr g&ouml;rn&uuml;&#351;leri we kyn&ccedil;ylyklary&#328;
&ouml;smegi bilen bellenil&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Cerarawsyz
kolitde&nbsp;<b>kolektomi&yacute;a&nbsp;</b>- i&ccedil;eg&auml;ni&#328;
k&ouml;p b&ouml;legini a&yacute;yrmak &uuml;&ccedil;in a&#351;akdakylar
bellenil&yacute;&auml;r:&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>&ccedil;i&#351;en i&ccedil;eg&auml;ni&#328;
g&uuml;&yacute;&ccedil;li &ccedil;i&#351;megi we ulalmagy;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>diwaryny&#328; de&#351;ilmegi;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>k&ouml;p&ccedil;&uuml;likle&yacute;in gan akma;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>deslapky &uuml;&yacute;tge&#351;meleri&#328; we karsinomy&#328;
&ouml;s&uuml;&#351;i.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Mundan ba&#351;ga-da, bir
hepd&auml;ni&#328; i&ccedil;inde derman bejergisi gowula&#351;ma&yacute;an agyr
&yacute;araly kolit &uuml;&ccedil;in kolektomi&yacute;a h&ouml;d&uuml;rlenip
bilner.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Kesgitli &ccedil;i&#351;mende
operasi&yacute;a doly bejergini berme&yacute;&auml;r, &#351;onu&#328;
&uuml;&ccedil;in adat&ccedil;a konserwatiw bejergini&#328; netijesiz bolan
kyn&ccedil;ylyklaryny bejermek &uuml;&ccedil;in ulanyl&yacute;ar:</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>p&auml;sgel&ccedil;iligi&#328; &ouml;smegi bilen
i&ccedil;eg&auml;ni&#328; l&yacute;umenini&#328; daralmagy;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>i&ccedil;ege we be&yacute;leki i&ccedil;ki organlary&#328;
arasynda patologiki ge&ccedil;elgeleri&#328; emele gelmegi;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>garyn bo&#351;lugynda absesleri&#328; &ouml;s&uuml;&#351;i;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>i&ccedil;ege diwaryny&#328; ganamagy &yacute;a-da
&yacute;arylmagy.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Hirurgiki operasi&yacute;a
usulyny sa&yacute;lamak, &yacute;&uuml;ze &ccedil;ykan
&ccedil;yl&#351;yrymlylyga baglydyr:&nbsp;<b>absesleri&#328; drenajy,
i&ccedil;eg&auml;ni&#328; t&auml;sir eden &yacute;erlerini a&yacute;yrmak,
&#351;ar dilasi&yacute;asy&nbsp;</b>.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
